{"tid":908930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺香港其實好多靚女, 只係唔識打扮?","createTime":"2018-11-20T03:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T03:21:18.000Z","uid":67294,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4583374cf050a37c1b0447a4b4ed56b4011394","tid":908930,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"之前去日本, 10個9個都係口罩妹, 之後一堆成吋厚既粉, 短裙蘿蔔腿<br />\n<br />\n相反香港其實好多靚女, 好耐之前就發覺港女多數都有對美腿<br />\n依家班00後仲進化到有返啲波路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奈可好多香港人好介意人點睇, 打扮一年四季一式一樣, tee牛仔短褲<br />\n髮型就來來去去都係長直髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講, 港女既外表係靠天生既本錢, 但其他地方就算樣衰都會靠打扮搭救有份啲氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}